                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1022">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to <gloss
                            type="to">Minister for Foreign Affairs of Siam</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1911-02-28">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 28, 1911</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I have the honor to inform Your Royal Highness that the American minister at
                    Bangkok, Mr. Hamilton King, has been designated as special representative of the
                    President of the United States on the occasion of the cremation of the remains
                    of His Late Majesty Chulalongkorn, and to request that he may be favorably
                    received in such capacity.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Knox.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
